# Private local-only files that must never be committed to this
# public repo. The `.wav` originals and the .docx/.pdf dist formats
# are published via different channels (MP3 demos are committed; raw
# WAV originals and dist formats are not).

# Lossless audio originals — only MP3 demos are published.
*.wav

# Distribution formats — the manual is the .md files here; .docx/.pdf
# builds are local artefacts only.
*.docx
*.pdf

# Editor / OS cruft
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
